# Database Patterns

## Drizzle + Neon
- Use `createDb()` from `@sofi/db` — it handles connection setup
- Use `{ client: sql, schema }` syntax for Drizzle (neon-http driver v1)
- For seeds/migrations, use tagged template: `sql\`SELECT ...\`` (not function calls)

## Dynamic pages
- All pages that query the DB MUST have `export const dynamic = "force-dynamic"`
- This prevents build-time errors when DATABASE_URL is not available

## Schema
- 5 tables: projects, artworks, furniture, inquiries, settings
- All content tables have: id, slug (unique), title, coverUrl, gallery (jsonb), featured, publishedAt, createdAt, updatedAt
- Settings uses key-value pattern with jsonb value column

## Image URLs
- Store Vercel Blob URLs in coverUrl and gallery fields
- Gallery is `jsonb` typed as `string[]`
